    {
      "id": "work_3179e0b6b52d80f683dcc877a08f8feb",
      "title": "彭城李記 | 四季好虾,时时好味",
      "desc": "烧烤大排档品牌全案策划设计",
      "cover": "images/uploads/cover_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb.jpg",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "h2",
          "html": "项目类型：餐饮品牌从 0 到 1 全案"
        },
        {
          "type": "h2",
          "html": "服务内容：品牌策略定位 | 视觉系统设计 | 空间落地统筹 | 物料全链设计"
        },
        {
          "type": "h2",
          "html": "全案统筹：林嘉雍"
        },
        {
          "type": "h2",
          "html": "创作时间：2025 年"
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "小龙虾作为国民级餐饮品类，已形成「小龙虾 +」的成熟经营模式，江苏作为全国小龙虾门店第一大省、产量 TOP5 省份，赛道竞争已进入白热化阶段。绝大多数小龙虾品牌陷入同质化困局：视觉上扎堆市井风、工业风、国潮风，千店一面；经营上受季节性限制严重，难以形成全年稳定的消费心智；体验上只聚焦「吃」的功能，忽略了当下年轻人对情绪价值、社交场景的核心需求。"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_1.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_2.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_3.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_4.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_5.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_6.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_7.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_8.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_9.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "放弃行业通用的市井风、工业风路线，锁定 「山野聆风，空谷回响」为品牌核心主题，打造「都市山野乌托邦」的差异化定位，构建「五感沉浸式体验」品牌壁垒："
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_10.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_11.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_12.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_13.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_14.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_15.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_16.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_17.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_18.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_19.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_20.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这是一场关于逃离、回归与共鸣的实践。于城市喧阗中，辟得一隅山野。风过留声，是自然在聆听；美食当前，是味蕾被治愈。我们懂都市年轻人的压力与孤独，懂他们对山野的向往、对真诚交流的渴望。于是我们把山野搬进城市，把四季好虾端上餐桌，用炭火的温热、龙虾的鲜香、自然的肌理，搭建一个能释放自我、畅所欲言的乌托邦。"
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "在这里，你可以暂且关闭世界的杂音，侧耳倾听 —— 听风穿过空谷，听炭火亲吻食材，听好友间毫无保留的畅谈。聆听本身即是治愈，举杯碰撞便是回响。四季好虾，时时好味；山野临风，空谷回响，这便是彭城李記。"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_21.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_22.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_23.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_24.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_25.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "围绕「山野自然 + 松弛治愈 + 年轻质感」三大核心，摒弃传统龙虾店的厚重、喧闹的视觉风格，以简约、原生、富有呼吸感的设计语言，传递品牌「都市山野乌托邦」的核心定位，实现策略与视觉的高度统一。"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_26.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_27.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_28.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_29.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>色彩系统</strong>以自然原生的大地色系为核心，打造低饱和度、高质感的色彩体系，还原山野的松弛与治愈感："
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_30.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "images/uploads/content_3179e0b6-b52d-80f6-83dc-c877a08f8feb_31.jpg"
        },
